Reasoning: The paper focuses on image editing using GANs and classical image processing techniques to modify image memorability. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of GANs also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the study of the impact of conventional photo-editing tools on memorability prediction suggests a possible inclusion in the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
